{"tid":736315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞官員「講粵語」遭猛批, 「講華語運動」組織: \"公共場合不應說方言\"","createTime":"2018-07-10T06:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T15:23:48.000Z","uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"540d9b21f4af321fdea909c901ce8e261a59d603","tid":736315,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"（吉隆坡9日訊）新任交通部長陸兆福日前到988電視台，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因接受粵語採訪</strong></span>，而引起&ldquo;馬來西亞講華語運動&rdquo;組織非議，並表明部長的舉動令人感到失望，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>強烈譴責尊貴的交通部長不用華語發表談話，令華文教育界倍感挫折。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/chinese-180709-b1-noresize1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fchinese-180709-b1-noresize1.jpg&h=f3938dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，此貼文昨日上傳后，引起網民的迴響，有人認同，也有人打臉這組織，認為這組織在雞<br />\n蛋里挑骨頭，畢竟陸兆福到訪的時段都是以粵語為主，講粵語並沒有任何不妥，況且因為類似<br />\n組織的打壓，越來越少人學習方言。一些網民認為，&ldquo;馬來西亞講華語運動&rdquo;組織反應過度，並認為這是個人的選擇，沒有對或錯。<br />\n<br />\n該組織認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">粵語只是廣府人的母語</span>，我國最大籍貫群卻是福建人和客家人，馬來西亞講華語運動多年以來，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所有的華人部長在公開場合都用華語，以配合華教的華語推廣運動</span></strong></span>，而希望部長正視問題。&ldquo;馬來西亞講華語運動的成立從來都不是為了消滅方言。我們的立場是，各籍貫之間應說華語，以示尊重，因為並不是所有的華裔都明白同一種方言，而華語確實是大多數華裔的共同語言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;這家電台（988）是打著中文電台的旗號，並非粵語電台，意思是聽眾群當中，也許有不諳粵<br />\n語的，所以我們才認為粵語不應成為此次訪問的使用語言。&rdquo;該組織說，許多人抨擊該組織要消滅方言是不正確的，因該組織大多數的執委都能說得一口流利的自家方言，甚至有的在也在積極推廣講方言。該組織說，他們不能強迫不同籍貫的人說一樣的方言，所以若涉及跨籍貫，<span style=\"color: red;\">華語應成為媒介語，並相信方言和華語是可以共存的。</span>"},{"pid":"17e016afe36a388adcfa0c3effcd4f5e9a0e9d35","tid":736315,"uid":53060,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/chinese-180709-b2-noresize1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fchinese-180709-b2-noresize1.jpg&h=191550af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民反應: 為什麼要學香港?"},{"pid":"d603b6f8d641b58f871cc9db365b646f47359db6","tid":736315,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"支那組織？"},{"pid":"7e83aef08864a60c7ea7aeb3b174559795060260","tid":736315,"uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"資料來源: <a href=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/20180709/%E9%9D%9E%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%B8%E5%85%86%E7%A6%8F%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E8%AA%AA%E7%B2%B5%E8%AA%9E-%E8%AC%9B%E8%8F%AF%E8%AA%9E%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E8%87%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2F20180709%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%2585%2586%25E7%25A6%258F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E8%25AA%259E-%25E8%25AC%259B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25AA%259E%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%2589%2F&d=enb%2FEwpyllMVguTJkK%2FrRLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=fdd300eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinapress.com.my/20180709/%E9%9D%9E%E8%AD%B0%E9%99%B8%E5%85%86%E7%A6%8F%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0%E8%AA%AA%E7%B2%B5%E8%AA%9E-%E8%AC%9B%E8%8F%AF%E8%AA%9E%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%93%E8%87%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n马来西亚讲华语运动 Malaysian Speak Mandarin Movement:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/msmm4u/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmsmm4u%2F&d=enb%2FEwpyllMVguTJkK%2FrRLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=c7b875c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/msmm4u/</a>"},{"pid":"a5dd75a84ad1bd4c24cf5345437f0337715f0aca","tid":736315,"uid":44171,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T07:05:01.000Z","msg":"馬拉幾時黎多次排華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji